  <entry>
    <title>&lt;프로그래머스&gt; 홀수 vs 짝수</title>
    <link href="http://mjae404.github.io/2024/05/07/programmers-052/"/>
    <id>http://mjae404.github.io/2024/05/07/programmers-052/</id>
    <published>2024-05-07T05:48:36.000Z</published>
